             sworn.</p>
               <p>On the second of July I lost the things mentioned in the indictment out of an upper drawer in a bureau in the parlour; I saw them a little before twelve; soon after I saw the prisoner in the room, he was in a closet when I first saw him; upon my coming in, he ran into the court; I ran after him and called to the neighbours to stop him, and he was soon taken.</p>
